_sText:
This is a second version of one of my older css-maps. That's why it isn't as good as my newest maps but I decided to distribute this map more because it's still quite good.

Terrorists and counter-terrorists have came by a small river to the old watermill.
Terrorists have to blow up the old watermill.
Counter-terrorists have to prevent them.
And try to find my little easter-egg and that isn't that guy in the truck. :P

Thanks to Syntax Terror for creating the bot-file and to iwannamap.com for great help with mapping.
